rows.label: qst700401_msg0001
rows.name:
Momo... Are you perhaps
quite skilled fighters, mo?

rows.label: qst700401_msg0002
rows.name:
Morumo is the chairman of this
shopping ward, mo. I've seen many,
many people, mo. So I can tell, mo.

rows.label: qst700401_msg0003
rows.name:
Your eyes hold the sparkle
of heroes, mo! I've decided
it just now, mo!!

rows.label: qst700401_msg0004
rows.name:
Do you know that Gogols have settled
in the Pilgrims' Springland Peln, mo?
It's become a very bad situation, mo.

rows.label: qst700401_msg0005
rows.name:
Everyone can't rest at the oasis anymore, mo.
We can't use the usual transport route either,
and we're forced to take a huge detour, mo.

rows.label: qst700401_msg0006
rows.name:
In other words... Business
is finished, mooooo!!!!

rows.label: qst700401_msg0007
rows.name:
Everyone is in a lot of trouble, mo. Morumo
is also in a lot of trouble, mo. Tears are
streaming, my pillow is soaked, mo!

rows.label: qst700401_msg0008
rows.name:
Please, mo. I want you to drive
the Gogols from the oasis, mo.
I'll reward you properly, mo!

rows.label: qst700401_msg0009
rows.name: Seeing you as heroes, I beg of you, mo!

rows.label: qst700401_msg0101
rows.name:
The oasis belongs to everyone, mo.
It's not just for the Gogols, mo.

rows.label: qst700401_msg0102
rows.name:
Please, mo. I want you to
drive away the Gogols, mo.
I'll reward you properly, mo!

rows.label: qst700401_msg0103
rows.name: Seeing you as heroes, I beg of you, mo!

rows.label: qst700401_msg0201
rows.name: Momo? You found the Gogol boss, mo?

rows.label: qst700401_msg0202
rows.name:
Morumo has seen it before, mo!
The one that's the bossiest and
biggest in the pack, mo.

rows.label: qst700401_msg0203
rows.name:
It's always on high ground,
looking down on us, mo. It
lacks humility, mo, hmph, mo.

rows.label: qst700401_msg0204
rows.name:
Please, mo! I want you to
punish it somehow, mo!
